OL,3,CCross-party inquiry to explore suicide
OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,FThe Inquiry will explore how
OL,7,Finvestment in suicide prevention could
OL,8,Fbe shared more effectively across
OL,9,Fgovernment departments including
OL,10,FHealth, Communities, Justice,
OL,11,FEducation and the Economy ` reflecting
OL,12,Fthe reality that many of the pressures
OL,13,Fdriving suicidal crisis originate far
OL,14,Fbeyond clinical services.
OL,16,FSpeaking ahead of the launch of the
OL,17,FInquiry, Orlaithi Flynn SF MLA, Chair
OL,18,Fof the All-Party Group on Suicide
OL,19,FPrevention, said:
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
