OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1768903439
OL,3,CCross-party inquiry to explore suicide
OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,F"Every death by suicide is a
OL,7,Fdevastating loss, and the fact that
OL,8,F290 people died in 2024 demands more
OL,9,Fthan words ` it demands action. That
OL,10,Fis why I am bringing forward proposals
OL,11,Ffor cross-departmental suicide
OL,12,Fprevention training, so that public
OL,13,Fservices across the system are better
OL,14,Fequipped to recognise risk and respond
OL,15,Fearlier.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
