OL,3,CCross-party inquiry to explore suicide
OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,F"But training alone is not enough if
OL,7,Fthe services people are referred into
OL,8,Fare unstable or under-funded. This
OL,9,FInquiry is about making sure our
OL,10,Ffunding structures match the reality
OL,11,Fof how prevention works in
OL,12,Fcommunities, and that responsibility
OL,13,Ffor protecting life is genuinely
OL,14,Fshared across government, not left to
OL,15,Fthe Department for Health."
OL,17,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt MLA, has
OL,18,Fwelcomed the launch and said:
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@[O]
