OL,3,CCross-party inquiry to explore suicide
OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,F"Suicide prevention cannot be
OL,7,Fdelivered by one department alone. The
OL,8,Ffactors that place people at risk span
OL,9,Fhealth, housing, education, justice,
OL,10,Fcommunity safety and economic
OL,11,Fpressures.
OL,13,F"I welcome this Inquiry. It is right
OL,14,Fthat we continue to learn from
OL,15,Ffrontline organisations as we shape
OL,16,Ffuture approaches."
