OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,FSarah O'Toole, Executive Director of
OL,7,FSamaritans Ireland, said:
OL,9,F"Every death to suicide is one too
OL,10,Fmany, and we must remember that behind
OL,11,Fevery statistic is a person and a
OL,12,Ffamily and community grieving.
OL,14,F"Our Lost Futures research shows
OL,15,Fclearly that many of the pressures
OL,16,Fdriving suicidal distress sit outside
OL,17,Fthe health system ` including poverty,
OL,18,Finsecure housing and financial strain.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
