OL,3,CCross-party inquiry to explore suicide
OL,4,Cprevention measures
OL,6,F"If we are serious about prevention,
OL,7,Fwe must invest earlier and more
OL,8,Fconsistently in the communities
OL,9,Fcarrying the greatest burden. As
OL,10,FSecretariat to the APG on Suicide
OL,11,FPrevention, Samaritans is proud to
OL,12,Fsupport this Inquiry and ensure that
OL,13,Fevidence from frontline services helps
OL,14,Fshape practical, long-term solutions."
